OL,3,CWildlife charity launches #250,000
OL,4,Cappeal for new nature reserve
OL,6,FA wildlife charity has launched a
OL,7,Fmajor fundraising campaign to buy and
OL,8,Frestore a new nature reserve to give
OL,9,F"struggling species" the "help they
OL,10,Fdesperately need."
OL,12,FCheshire Wildlife Trust is calling on
OL,13,Fthe public to help raise #250,000 by
OL,14,Fthe end of September 2026 to purchase
OL,15,FFox Hill in the Todd Brook Valley - a
OL,16,F58-acre site nestled in the Peak
OL,17,FDistrict.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
