OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777457195
OL,3,CWildlife charity launches #250,000
OL,4,Cappeal for new nature reserve
OL,6,FThey have described purchasing Fox
OL,7,FHill as an "unmissable opportunity" as
OL,8,Fthe site sits directly adjacent to the
OL,9,Fcharity's existing Aldred's Lea Nature
OL,10,FReserve and is just 300 meters from
OL,11,Ftheir Greenbooth site.
OL,13,FThe trust says, if the appeal is
OL,14,Fsuccessful, it would bring 118 acres
OL,15,Fof land near Bollington under its care
OL,16,Fand create a connected corridor where
OL,17,Fnature can be protected and allowed to
OL,18,Frecover.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
