CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777457195
OL,3,CWildlife charity launches #250,000
OL,4,Cappeal for new nature reserve
OL,6,FBen Gregory, Director of Nature
OL,7,FRecovery at Cheshire Wildlife Trust,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Fox Hill has extraordinary
OL,9,Fpotential for wildlife.
OL,11,F"To the untrained eye, this is a
OL,12,Fbreathtaking landscape, however, over
OL,13,Fthe last few decades there have been
OL,14,Fmarked declines in bird populations.
OL,16,F"Wildlife is struggling due to habitat
OL,17,Floss and wild spaces being smaller and
OL,18,Fmore fragmented. Species like lapwing
OL,19,Fare disappearing and without
OL,20,Fintervention, we could lose the unique
OL,21,Fcry of our curlew too.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
